---
title: "Sequence Diagram (Analysis) - Adjust Salary"
config:
  theme: neutral
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant B as SalaryScreen<br>«boundary»
    participant C as AdjustSalaryController<br>«control»
    participant W as Worker<br>«entity»
    participant H as SalaryHistory<br>«entity»

    User->>B: select option 2/3, enter code + amount
    B->>C: status, code, amount
    C->>W: find worker by code
    alt code exists and amount valid
        C->>W: update salary (+/- amount)
        C->>H: create history record (UP/DOWN)
        C-->>B: success
        B-->>User: "Salary adjusted successfully!"
    else invalid
        C-->>B: error message
        B-->>User: show error
    end
